{
  "stem": "5639.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Rossner had his flat either on the first or on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were just opposite the station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I glued my eye to this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I saw a sea of human faces.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Not a sound coming there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The distance was less that from one side of street and here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Not a sound.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I didn't know whether it's real or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And gradually, I recognized some faces.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they were immobile.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And as I had a very narrow field of vision, I had the impression that they are only faces, because I didn't see the bodies.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the faces were immobile.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The heads didn't move.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was an eerie feeling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then, obviously, I have fainted again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the next thing that woke me out-- up was, I fainted, and I think I induced the fainting on me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the next thing that woke me up was banging and shouting, and banging at the floor-- at the door of that room, and trying to prise them open.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But, of course, they couldn't, because it was--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--blocked with mountain of metal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they was given up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what actually woke me up were voices.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember whose voices, but I knew them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In German, she must be there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She is there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they pushed the door, and they fished me out from there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What was the-- a very telling situation, and particularly telling, as far as human behavior is concerned, that by that time, August '43, politically, Italy was defeated.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Germans did not reenter Italy yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mussolini was hanged already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And here was talk that Rossner intends to open another shop where only hundred families will go there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He already knew that he can't save the whole ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
